Self-Interest Is the Lever that Moves People

7
00:00:33,109 --> 00:00:37,429
The art of asking people for help depends
on your ability to understand the person you

8
00:00:37,429 --> 00:00:41,939
are dealing with, and to not confuse your
needs with theirs. Know that even the most

9
00:00:41,939 --> 00:00:46,489
powerful person is locked inside needs of
his own, and that if you make no appeal to

10
00:00:46,490 --> 00:00:51,420
