be able to exercise charity, mercy, and justice,

46
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:37,229
which are their ways of feeling superior to
you:

47
00:03:37,229 --> 00:03:41,768
Because of their superior position, if you
ask this person for help, you emphasize their

48
00:03:41,769 --> 00:03:46,759
power and position. The only requirement from
you is that all of this is done in public,

49
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:52,079
the more public, the better. It is truly their
pleasure to give and to be seen giving. They

50
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:56,410
are dying to fund your project, to introduce
you to powerful people—this is the wine

51
00:03:56,409 --> 00:03:59,829
that intoxicates them.
